data.description:
WHY RENT! Buy now this Super cute 2-bedroom home. Check out the list of MAJOR improvements; Newer A/C and furnace, roof, siding, all installed in the last few years. The kitchen was just totally updated with new custom white cabinetry, sink, flooring, appliances. Newer flooring throughout rest of home. Main floor laundry. An area for a office space bright light. Wait to you see the fenced in back yard, over 1/2 lot, perfect for kids and pets keep them safe but plenty of space to romp and roam. Huge deck nice area to entertain and BBQ, Yard level nice place for pool, swing set and a great garden spot. There is Additional driveway/parking on the right side of home, a place to put that camper or boat or just cars if needed. Oversize garages keep your car out of bad weather, and plenty of storage.
Hurry now your payment will be less than renting and have those pets you always wanted. Control your own financial destiny!
